	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So the goal is to avoid the blocks that come at you? I am not too fond of this idea because it removes two things I consider essential: the ability to turn left and right and the freedom to explore.
<br />
<br />It should be possible to come up with some other kind of gameplay that does not require objects to be placed in the maze... You can have a gun and shooting walls is definitely a possibility, so maybe something interesting can be made with those elements.
<br />
<br />I do <strong>want</strong> to add objects eventually, but there would be at most 2 or 3 objects in a room, otherwise the speed would drop too much.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


